-------------------------
CHESSX SYSTEM REQUIRMENTS
-------------------------

This application is going to reproduce the clasic chess board game.

There will be two players. One must be a human player and the other
must be a human player or a AI player. The first player will decide
which color pieces he or she will play. The other player will
automatically recieve the other color to play. The player with the
white pieces will have the first turn of the game.

There will be a board with the dimentions of 8x8 of squares. The
squares may or may not own pieces.

Each player has ownership of 8 pawns, 2 bishops, 2 knights, 2 rooks,
1 Queen, and 1 King. They will all be placed in the standard squares
stated in the chess rules.
